We’ll be visiting Kentucky June 8th – 10th to launch our partnership with Heidelberg Distributing!

The Bruery® & Bruery Terreux® are set to launch statewide distribution in Kentucky starting June 8 through Heidelberg Kentucky. This will be the first time our portfolio of experimental and barrel-aged beers will be available in the state! Kentucky is the 28th state to be added to our national distribution footprint.
